This is the Geometry Dash portable Demonlist extension!

Just enter the hardest maps you have completed, and view them in a nice ranked list!

There is also an overview tab / profile tab where some cool stats and stuff can be seen!

All levels are now store locally by default, to store them accross different computers, select the "sync" option in the level's storage option


Update v2.0+: 
- Added the settings menu
- Added ability to export and import lists via files.
- Levels can now also be stored locally or in synced. By default, all levels are stored locally, to store them accross browsers, you can select "sync" in the levels storage options.
- Fixed bugs / improvements
- This extension is now using react
